  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Collaboration between the surgeon and the anesthesiologist is key for delivering a safe
      pheochromocytoma surgery. This study aims to establish the collective performance of
      surgeon-anesthesiologist team by quantifying the relationship between their previous
      collaborations and patient complications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
